{"tid":2498459,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"破曉行動三青年被控非法集結 警員朱秋明被質疑證供「加鹽加醋」致出現三個不同版本","createTime":"2021-04-21T07:36:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T10:32:54.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"68efd4a8b63b134f05dfdee40bef8e00e4ca478d","tid":2498459,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T07:36:08.000Z","msg":"朱秋明:<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Bv2dAoQTEgE_Zhrgs7mUJuzwmwU=/802x1202/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LRNLQCBN3ZD45GII5QW6PC6AQU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FBv2dAoQTEgE_Zhrgs7mUJuzwmwU%3D%2F802x1202%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLRNLQCBN3ZD45GII5QW6PC6AQU.jpg&h=b2f0ad2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n市民前年11月發起大三罷「破曉行動」，各區多人被捕，其中有社工、補習導師與學生三人被控在荃灣參與非法集結及違反蒙面法。三名被告不認罪，案件今於西九龍裁判法院開審。警員庭上作供時，被發現內容與其記事冊紀錄及書面供詞不符，遭辯方質疑他「加鹽加醋」以致出現三個版本的證供。警員則堅稱三個說法相同，只屬文字表達問題。<br />\n<br />\n警員19757朱秋明今供稱，當晚接報指沙咀道及大河道交界多次被人用雜物堵路。朱到場清理路障時，發現除雜物外，連沙咀道遊樂場內的龍門架都被搬出並放置馬路上，令交通受阻。而荃新天地商場外有過百人在行人路聚集，大部份人身穿黑色衫褲，其間叫囂並高呼「五大訴求口，缺一不可」及「光復香港」等口號。<br />\n<br />\n晚上8時許，朱正在警車上候命，從通訊機得知有警員曾向聚集人士發出警告，指他們正參與未經批准集結。未幾警方進行驅散行動，朱隨隊到沙咀道與禾笛街交界進行包抄，其間看見沙咀道有一群人士分別向禾笛街及眾安街方向逃跑，有人尖叫，情況混亂。<br />\n<br />\n此時，朱發現一名戴黑色口罩的白衣男子向荃新天地方向「搏命跑」，並手持白色物品。朱懷疑他有份參與非法集結，故進行追截並警告「企喺度，唔好走」。當朱追近至與男子相距3米時，男子跑入荃新天地中庭，再轉出新村街逃走。及後朱用雙手拉著該男子背囊，並把他制服在地上。朱於庭上確認該男子為被告。當時葉手持一包索帶，又曾「揈手揈腳」掙扎。<br />\n<br />\n辯方質疑，朱在主問時描述追截的過程，與他在警員記事冊及書面供詞中所述的，分別為三個不同版本。朱曾於記事冊指，被告在其警告下仍繼續往新村街方向跑；但朱的書面供詞卻指被告跑入荃新天地中庭，而當朱追近被告3米距離時，被告再突然轉出新村街方向逃走。辯方續指，供詞不符是因為朱事後「加鹽加醋」；警員否認，辯稱只屬文字表達問題。<br />\n<br />\n惟朱在盤問下又供稱，被告從被追截至被捕時均無戴眼鏡，但辯方呈上被告在警署所拍的照片，卻顯示被告當時戴眼鏡。朱反駁謂：「唔代表（被捕）嗰時有戴。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210421/OJTMGFDS25DZFKNSMAWSQ3RUSQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210421%2FOJTMGFDS25DZFKNSMAWSQ3RUSQ%2F&d=Hmcjt6vcQR8GyvD5m8y4dPulYLG83ImyreQ67A6WOt4%3D&h=5938a46e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210421%2FOJTMGFDS25DZFKNSMAWSQ3RUSQ%2F&h=59a6c3f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210421/OJTMGFDS25DZFKNSMAWSQ3RUSQ/</a>"},{"pid":"bbadae9cb80ed6f84058157ad4a62647f1624869","tid":2498459,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T07:37:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6f0909b75de5976142f335dfd131e3ef976d235","tid":2498459,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T07:42:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c285bab11e736362814d6da1195302419a3943f","tid":2498459,"uid":77196,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T07:42:31.000Z","msg":"紅官：控方證人誠實可靠"},{"pid":"316990d218208c6907ab3ca7ce20d8bda4aea104","tid":2498459,"uid":54593,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T07:43:46.000Z","msg":"黑警又作故仔"},{"pid":"1890694272269f4bf1e8ff401f3f57b07f10f7ca","tid":2498459,"uid":121401,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T07:45:12.000Z","msg":"好大包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"599faafaf7c61d9b45501fd33c206c4a2a25ddd8","tid":2498459,"uid":238920,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"1890694272269f4bf1e8ff401f3f57b07f10f7ca","tid":2498459,"uid":121401,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T07:45:12.000Z","msg":"好大包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T07:51:34.000Z","msg":"gay佬都唔緊要,我份人好開明<br />\n但你人獸戀我真係接受唔到"},{"pid":"97a8cf15045805573a70d9229c783f61b7f434e9","tid":2498459,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T08:50:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fdff1d9db1075e651a9c1a7b7dbc1fc358de982","tid":2498459,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T09:14:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cc53ad7df2a3a94bfc5a8221fc4a5d464427192","tid":2498459,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T09:58:05.000Z","msg":"辯方質疑，數警制服首被告時<span class=\"red\">出動警棍狂毆</span>，他在迫不得已的情況下，只好擺動手腳保護自己。辯方又指，警員在記事冊、供詞及主問階段竟供出<span class=\"red\">被告逃跑的不同版本</span>，質疑他事後「加鹽加醋」。惟警員通通否認。<br />\n<br />\n朱在辯方盤問下坦認，當時已連續執勤逾 36 小時，身體相當疲倦。他表示，群眾向他迎面跑來時，情況十分混亂。他不知道同僚有否施放催淚氣體，亦沒有留意是否有除首被告外的<span class=\"red\">白衣人逃跑</span>。<br />\n<br />\n辯方表示，關於首被告逃走的路線，朱供出了 3 個不同版本。<br />\n1. 左轉入新村街方向逃走；<br />\n2. 向朱(黑警)迎面跑來，並向荃新天地中庭逃走，及後突然轉身走向新村街<br />\n3. 右轉入荃新天地，朱(黑警)追至其身旁時，他轉身走向新村街。<a href=\"https://w